Package: BBSS
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Blind Source Separation
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-02-07
Author: Joshua Lukemire
Maintainer: Joshua Lukemire <joshua.lukemire@emory.edu>
Description: This package implements covariate-adjusted Bayesian blind source separation approaches for cross-sectional and longitudinal data, with the option to also control for site effects. This current version of the package is still in development.
